Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:58.62,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}夢のつづき　追いかけていたはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:58.62,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}Yume no tsuzuki oikaketeita hazu nanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:04.96,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Yet I faltered over others while walking this thin, winding path.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:04.96,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}曲がりくねった　細い道　人につまずく
