Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.07,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That thing called "reality"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.07,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…現実ってやつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.07,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Genjitsu tte yatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.40,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just want to scream out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.40,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叶えるために　生きてるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.40,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kanaeru tame ni ikiterundatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.82,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"I'm only living to fulfill my wish." Can you hear me?
